<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Template Manager</title>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
	<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
  </head>

  <body style="background-color: ">
  <header>
  </header>
  <main style="padding-left: 0;">
  <div class="container" style="padding-top: 5%;">
      <div class="row">
      	<div class="col m2"></div>
        <div class="col s12 m8">
          <div class="card blue-grey darken-1 horizontal">
          	
          	<div class="card-image">
        		<!--<img src="https://lorempixel.com/100/190/nature/6">
        		<i class="material-icons dp48">settings</i>-->
      		</div>
            
            <div class="card-stacked">
            	<div class="card-content white-text">
            		<span class="card-title">Setup Wizard: API Credentials (1/3)</span>
              <p>Template Manager relies on <a style="color:white; text-decoration: underline;" href="https://github.com/K43GFX/templatemanager#installation-of-i-tee-virtualbox-api">I-Tee-Virtualbox API service</a>, you should already have that installed and initialized in case you followed our documentation. Please insert API server IP and port.</p><br>

              <p>Click "Verify settings" to make sure API is reached, otherwise you have to reconfigure API credentials afterwards.</p><br>

            	  <div class="row">
        <%= form_for Setting.first_or_create!, :url => {:action => "apiupdate"}, remote: true do |f| %>
      <div class="row">
    <div class="input-field col s6">
      <%= f.text_field :apiserver, { class: "validate", required: true, autocomplete: "off" } %>
      <label>API host address</label>
    </div>
        <div class="input-field col s6">
      <%= f.text_field :apiport, { class: "validate", required: true, autocomplete: "off" } %>
      <label>API port</label>
    </div>
      </div>
      <%= f.submit "Verify settings", {class: "waves-effect waves-light btn", remote: true} %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
            	</div>
        	<div class="card-action">
          		<a href="<%= setup_rdp_path %>">Next step >> Default RDP access configuration</a>
        	</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col m2"></div>
      </div>
</div>
  </main>
  </body>
</html>

<br>